1.docker compose is used for multi container environment
2.docker-compose uses yaml file syntax
3.docker-compose cli (commands to up and run the infrastructure from docker-compose)
4.like docker cli docker-compose cli also has similar commands 

a.docker-compose up to up the infrastructure
b.docker-compose down to down the infrastrcure
c.docker-cmpose logs
4.docker-compose ps to view process in compose containers
d.docker-compose top
etc

